  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"ijt2up8R\">除了刚术后几周的肿胀+疼痛这种物理上的难受，我个人感受最明显的还是精神上的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=745574193&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%B9%BB%E8%82%A2%E6%84%9F&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">幻肢感<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，术后一年内会经常有奇怪的不真实感（就像是很多人说的凉嗖嗖的感觉，不过对我来说更多的是瞬时几秒然后又消失）。幻肢感消失之前，穿女士内裤会很别扭，所以我那阵还是经常穿男士内裤，感觉会好很多。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
